title: November 2009 General Election Unofficial Results, VSBE
name: November 2009 General Election Unofficial Results, VSBE
description:
This data comes from the Virgina State Board of Elections. Data is a shapefile of the latest General Election results in the state of Virginia. The election took place November 3, 2009. This data is at the county level and includes information for governor, lieutenant governor, attorney general, and the general assembly. 

Uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.
